GSD.description:
openvswitch: switch from WARN to pr_warn

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.4.223 by commit 4175d6381f6f1c152a73183caf1c72b3d6909f31, it was introduced in version v3.14 by commit 44da5ae5fbea4686f667dc854e5ea16814e44c59. For more details please see the references link.
